We use the information you actively provide us about yourself, such as in creating or editing a profile or making a reservation, to complete your purchases and other requests, and to process, confirm, update and fulfill the travel and other products or services you request from us. In addition, we may use this information for the following:
To register and service your Dividend Miles account;
To administer and deliver the benefits of the various Dividend Miles programs;
To enhance or customize the products and services we, or other third parties as described below, provide to you (for example, at the explicit request of a Dividend Miles member, storing payment information to make subsequent purchases more convenient);
For internal operations such as information systems management, accounting, billing and audits,;
To contact you to respond to your questions or requests, to resolve issues, and/or to provide you technical support; and
To provide scheduled email newsletters, promotional or special offers such as sweepstakes and contests, and occasional mailings that we believe may be of interest to you.
We may use the information automatically collected from your computer or other devices for the following uses:
To improve our products and services;
To customize and enhance the user experience of our Sites and Services;
To administer, upgrade, and protect our Sites and Services, email servers, and other computer systems;
To analyze trends, track user movement and habits, and gather statistical information for aggregate use; and
To customize and serve advertising and other marketing communications that may be visible to you on our Sites and Services or elsewhere on the internet.
Please note that we may share information that we collect from and about you and your devices with our Dividend Miles partners, service providers and other third parties, as described in the 'Who we share your information with' section below.
